    (how are you ?$V_ACTUALLY (able ?to)|(capable ?of) ?$V_ACTUALLY $ENT_RI_JBO_HowCanStrictAction) |
    (how is it ?$V_ACTUALLY possible|feasible|conceivable for you ?to ?$V_ACTUALLY $ENT_RI_JBO_HowCanStrictAction) |
