    (you ?just like|love|adore|enjoy  ?(a|an|the) ?$V_VERY $ENT_RI_JBO_LikesStrictThing ?(right|(don\'t you))) |
	(are you happy|excited|proud ((?that you can)|((?that you are)|(about being)|(to ?be) ?$V_ACTUALLY able|capable ?(to|of)))|(to ?be) $ENT_RI_JBO_LikesStrictThing)
