   (am|are i|we ?$V_ACTUALLY ?(being|feeling) ?$V_VERY $ENT_GENERAL_DESCRIPTOR|$ENT_EMOTION) |
   ((do you think|believe)|(would you say) (i|we am|are)|i\'m|we\'re ?(being|feeling) ?$V_VERY $ENT_GENERAL_DESCRIPTOR|$ENT_EMOTION) |
