   (do you ?$V_ACTUALLY feel ?(like|(as if|though)) i\'m|we\'re|(i|we am|are) ?$V_ACTUALLY ?$V_VERY $ENT_GENERAL_DESCRIPTOR|$ENT_EMOTION)
){% intent='isUserDescriptor' %};

